Welcome to Connect Four. Read the following instructions to play the game, enjoy!

    Connect Four is a two-player game, where each player picks a colour and has tiles of this colour.
The first player to connect four tiles in a row - horizontal, vertical or diagonal - emerges the winner of the game.

Launch the game.
Decide who plays first and start the game by dropping a tile.
Both players alternate turns in dropping tiles until one player gets FOUR of their tiles in a row.
The first player to get FOUR tiles in a row wins.